dc_title_s: Neighborhood Associations City of Madison, WI 2017
dc_description_s: This data layer represents neighborhood association boundaries for the City of Madison, Wisconsin in 2017. [Location of City of Madison Neighborhood Associations. Boundaries are self reported and not determined by the City of Madison.This data layer is used by the City of Madison Neighborhood Associations and Development Information applications.]
uw_supplemental_s: Archived dataset at UW-Madison. For the most current version of this data please visit: https://data-cityofmadison.opendata.arcgis.com/
